snippet.title: Le Monde
snippet.description:
Bienvenue sur la chaîne YouTube du Monde. Chaque jour, des vidéos et des documentaires pour comprendre l'actualité. International, politique, sciences, histoire, pop culture... Rejoignez-nous pour y voir plus clair !

▶️ Tous les jours, les images incontournables de l'actualité

▶️ Chaque semaine, des documentaires explicatifs pour comprendre le monde

▶️ Nos enquêtes vidéo : des violences policières à la répression des Ouïgours, notre équipe enquête sur les sujets les plus chauds, grâce à des témoignages, images satellites, reconstitutions 3D et documents exclusifs

▶️ La série #Mappemonde, pour comprendre les grandes crises géopolitiques du XXIe siècle

▶️ La série #Flashback, dans les secrets des images qui ont changé le monde

Et bien plus ! N'hésitez pas à nous partager vos idées en commentaires sous les vidéos.

snippet.title: Juice Cannon™
snippet.description:
Juice Cannon is a Afrobeat Hip Hop Artist 
Born in Ogun State Nigeria, Raised in Brooklyn NY currently residing in New York City. 

In September 2017 he released the single "Naija Girls" from the mixtape "Sugarwater". "Naija Girls" was the first viral hit from Juice in the Afrobeats genre. In 2020, he released the Hip Hop track "Treesha" featuring Billy B, during the pandemic. 

The following year, Juice Canon released four projects with "Amapiano" from the EP "Live My Life 4" being the most successful song/video of that year. After a brief hiatus from music, he returned in 2023 with Marriott Hotels an R&B focused album with features from 3D'Natee, Anthiny King and Londa B.

snippet.title: Andrea B. Mendel - Buranello * Records -
snippet.description:
Super Tele Records and Pictures. 
Este canal es una máquina del tiempo que posee una magia sutil:
un cofre del tesoro que contiene los recuerdos más preciados del dúo musical FANTABEAT (Andrea Buranello & Fujiko Mine).
Las imágenes detrás de escena y los momentos que quedaron grabados en el corazón.
El concepto del inexorable paso del tiempo siempre nos ha fascinado:
especialmente Fujiko Mine quien siempre ha preferido vivir en mundos paralelos antes que enfrentar la realidad de tener que elegir entre la razón y el corazón.
Después de todo, todos viajamos juntos en el tiempo.
Y sólo nos queda hacer lo mejor que podemos para disfrutar de este increíble viaje.
La música nos salvó a los dos: nos dio ternura, complicidad y gran atención el uno hacia el otro.
¡Porque nadie está preparado para el amor, ni para lo que vendrá!

snippet.title: VOA Learning English
snippet.description:
Learn English with fun videos!

Learning English is VOA’s multimedia source of news and information for millions of English learners worldwide.

Learning English began as Special English, which Voice of America launched in 1959. Special English newscasts and features were a primary fixture of VOA’s international shortwave broadcasts for more than half a century. In 2014, our line of products was expanded to include more English teaching materials, and the service became known as Learning English.

Learners absorb American English through content drawn from U.S. and world news, Health and Lifestyle, Science and Technology, Arts and Culture, and other topics. Learners can build vocabulary, strengthen speaking skills and improve the ability to communicate for work, school and everyday life.

Audio programs and captioned videos - English in A Minute, Everyday Grammar TV and Learning English TV - are written using vocabulary at the upper-beginner and intermediate level.

snippet.title: HaiBunda
snippet.description:
Menjadi orang tua, khususnya bunda, tidaklah mudah. Perlu belajar untuk bisa mendidik dan merawat anak dengan baik. Seiring dengan perubahan zaman dan perkembangan teknologi informasi, tantangan menjadi orang tua pun semakin bertambah. Tidak hanya itu, begitu banyak informasi dan mitos-mitos yang beredar seputar permasalahan bunda.

Menyadari hal tersebut, Haibunda.com hadir sebagai media massa online yang memberikan informasi tepercaya seputar dunia parenting, kehamilan, menyusui, mom’s life baik dari para pakar maupun pengalaman bunda-bunda lainnya.

snippet.title: NSW Jewish Board of Deputies
snippet.description:
The NSW Jewish Board of Deputies is the official elected representative roof-body of the Jewish Community in New South Wales, with 55 major communal organisations as its constituents.

The Board leads, speaks and advocates on behalf of the NSW Jewish Community.

Our vision is a united NSW Jewish Community, adequately resourced, enjoying physical and political security as part of a harmonious, inclusive, democratic Australian society. 

To achieve this, we consistently perform the following:

Represent and advocate on behalf of the NSW Jewish Community

Ensure the political and physical security of the NSW Jewish Community.

Combat antisemitism and other forms of racism.

Increase understanding of Israel and its centrality to Jewish life.

Promote social inclusion of all segments of NSW society.

Maintain the unity and cohesion of the NSW Jewish Community.

Ensure continuity of a vibrant NSW Jewish Community.

snippet.title: Dua Lipa
snippet.description:
The official YouTube channel for Dua Lipa.

Born and raised in London to Kosovar-Albanian parents, Dua Lipa signed to Warner Records in 2015 releasing her self titled debut in 2017 which featured the hit singles, 'Be The One', 'IDGAF', 'Hotter Than Hell' & her first UK #1 hit 'New Rules'. 

Critical success soon followed as Dua Lipa picked up Brit Awards for 'Best Female Solo Artist' and 'Best British Breakthrough Act' as well as Grammy Awards for 'Best New Artist' and 'Best Dance Recording' for the track 'Electricity' in collaboration with Silk City.

Her second internationally acclaimed studio album 'Future Nostalgia' was released in 2020 and included the hit singles 'Don't Start Now, 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' and 'Levitating', with the remix album 'Club Future Nostalgia' following shortly after featuring guest appearances from 'Blackpink', 'Missy Elliott', 'Madonna' and 'Gwen Stefani'.

snippet.title: Rayvanny
snippet.description:
Raymond Shaban Mwakyusa (born 22 August 1993), better known by his stage name Rayvanny is a Tanzanian singer, songwriter, and The CEO of the Record label known as NEXT LEVEL MUSIC.

Rayvanny emerged in the spotlight with his debut song "Kwetu", which introduced him to the world. Later on, he released he grabbed attention with his hit song featuring Diamond Platnumz titled "Tetema" which grabbed different charts Worldwide. 

Rayvanny was mentioned by MTV Base among "Acts To Look Out For" in 2017 and also won Viewer's Choice Best New International Artist on BET Awards 2017.

Rayvanny has been the first AFRICAN ARTIST to perform at MTV EMA shows in late of 2021 with MALUMA, and he also  was the. first East African artist to win DIAFA AWARDS in late of 2022.

2. Jyada se jyada practice 
3. Practice se accuracy aayegi 
4. Jyada accuracy means , examination hall mein paper, kam waqt mein solve

snippet.title: Carmen Hajjar
snippet.description:
Carmen is regarded as one of the top experts in
etiquette and protocol with a huge following and a highly
interactive approach to training and education. Her passion
for this field, professional experience as an educator, extensive
training and certifications from the most reputed international
organizations gives Carmen an edge over her peers.
Over time Carmen developed a passion for etiquette
and protocol and traveled around the world to become an
internationally certified consultant, coach and trainer.
Carmen currently delivers various workshops for
corporates, one to one training sessions for individuals, as
well as group interactive sessions for adults and youth, in
Lebanon and the gulf.
Carmen has been interviewed by and has appeared as a
regular guest on local and International news
stations, newspapers and radios most notably OTV, LBC,
Radio Middle East (Montreal, CA), Annahar,
Aljamhouria, NBN, Voix du Liban, and many others.

snippet.title: A LA MODA CON JOSMIL Tu Revista Fashionista
snippet.description:
A LA MODA CON JOSMIL Tu Revista Fashionista 
Dedicado a la mujer vanguardista de hoy, donde podremos ver las mejores prendas, tendencias, peinados, maquillajes, cortes y colores de temporada con el asesoramiento de expertos. Entrevistas, tutoriales, maratones de videos y programas especiales de eventos relevantes al mundo de la moda como desfiles de modas, alfombras rojas y otros. Cuenta con secciones y capsulas dedicada a puntos estratégico de la moda y como impactan de manera positiva en la vida de la mujer de hoy.  Dichas secciones son: Rostros y Sombras, Diosas en Tacones, El Sofá Fashion, Siluetas, El Outfit de la Semana, , El Ciclo de la Moda y Las Frases de la Semana.
JOMIL LORENZO AQUINO
Productora y presentadora oficial del programa. Lic. en Comunicación Social mención Periodismo, egresada de la Universidad Autónoma de Santo Domingo (UASD). Locutora. Miembro del Colegio Dominicano de Periodistas (CDP). Diseñadora de Modas y Propietaria de la Tienda D` Jomil Decoraciones.

snippet.title: Shankar Mahadevan Academy
snippet.description:
Shankar Mahadevan Academy was founded in 2011 by Bollywood singer and composer, Shankar Mahadevan and technology entrepreneur, Sridhar Ranganathan to bring Indian music education to the masses.  Shankar Mahadevan Academy (SMA) is the first school for Indian music in the world to bring high-quality Indian music education through live, online classes.

Our mission is to spread the Joy of Music.

As of 2022, we have students in over 90 countries, as young as 2.5 to 92 ! We have conducted more than 400,000+ live, online classes and continue to offer live, online classes 24X7 with our expert instructors. At SMA, you can learn anything - from Hindustani Vocals, Carnatic Vocals, Movie Songs, Music for Children, Voice Gym, Guitar, Piano, Playback Singing, and more.

snippet.title: Ultimate Dream Family
snippet.description:
https://youtube.com/@suvankardas1987
Hello friends welcome to you our channel ULTIMATE DREAM FAMILY.
Thanks to all my subscribers and viewers for supporting me and 
reaching me about 4K subscribers.Here I published education, information, 
historical video that is current topics, trending video,trending shots,vlog etc.
আমার সকল সাবস্ক্রাইবার বন্ধুদের ও ভিউয়ার্সদের জানাই অসংখ্য ধন্যবাদ । 
আপনাদের সাপোর্টে আজ আমার 4কে সাবস্ক্রাইবার পূর্ণ হতে চলেছে।
আমি চারটি বিভাগে  ভিডিও  আপলোড করি।
1)দেশ-বিদেশে যে ঘটনা ঘটে চলেছে তার মধ্যে কিছু উল্লেখযোগ্য ঘটনা  তুলে ধরি। 
2)বছরের কিছু গুরুত্বপূর্ণ দিনের মাহাত্ম্য আলোচনা করি। 
3)আমার  সঙ্গে ঘটে যাওয়া কিছু ঘটনা আপনাদের কাছে তুলে ধরি।
4)আমার জমজ দুই কন্যার ও ছেলের নৃত্যের ভিডিও এই চ্যালেনে থাকে।
আমার তথ্যবহুল ও ইতিহাস আশ্রিত ভিডিওর মাধ্যমে আপনাদের কিছু
ফেরত দেওয়ার চেষ্টা করি।এখান থেকে যদি একজনেরও কোন উপকার  
হয় তাহলে নিজেকে ধন্য মনে করব।এভাবেই আপনার আমার সঙ্গে থাকুন আর
আমার ভিডিও গুলো দেখতে থাকুন। 
সবার মঙ্গল হোক সুস্থ থাকুন সবল থাকুন।ধন্যবাদ।

snippet.title: Matt Friend
snippet.description:
Matthew Friend is an old soul living inside a 26-year-old comedian/actor/impressionist's body. Matthew graduated from NYU’s Gallatin School in 2020, but his love of comedy and entertainment was sparked when he was four years old. He had watched Austin Powers (yes, as a four-year-old) and started mimicking the characters’ voices—and the rest was history. 

To date, Matthew has over two million followers across all social platforms: TikTok, Snap, Instagram, Twitter, and Facebook. He has appeared on The Howard Stern Show, the Today Show, Jimmy Kimmel Live, NBC’s New York Live TV, Good Day LA, Good Day NY, Good Morning Washington, and WGN. In 2019, Matthew won Kenan Thompson’s Ultimate Comedy Experience at Carolines on Broadway. Matthew performs at corporate events and does stand-up comedy throughout the country. Matthew’s repertoire includes more than 250 impressions ranging from Rami Malek to Timothee Chalamet. His favorite impression at the moment is Jennifer Coolidge.
